Showing unique numbers to each property in a search result using ROW_NUMBER().
⚖️ Trade-offs
Case	When to Use
🧮 ROW_NUMBER()	When you just want unique numbering, no skips.
🏆 RANK()	When you want to show equal rank for same values.
