Text
Copy code
GET /api/property/5
Authorization: Bearer token
Server does not remember previous request.
Each request sends token again.
Stateful Example
Traditional web apps using Session.
User logs in.
Server stores:
Copy code

SessionID
UserId
Login state
Next request uses stored session.
4️⃣ Comparison Table
Stateless
Stateful
