6️⃣ Trade-Off
Stateless Advantages
✔ Easy scaling
✔ Better performance in cloud
✔ Simpler server design
Stateless Disadvantages
❌ Client must send data every request
Stateful Advantages
✔ Server remembers user data
✔ Easier session handling
